courtorder_explain: Dear Google, page 2 item1a and item1b of the pdf file  
gives us the authority to remove the various webpages listed above on this  
submission template. Attached is a signed Federal Court Order for any and  
all sites promoting/infringing on our patent of "Gear Ring" (page 2, item1a  
& item1b)

Proof of my patent can be found on the URL below as well.

http://news.priorsmart.com/kinekt-design-v-mason-l4if/#pat-D639199

thank you for your help.
